{ Since the c-file is closed now, our queen sits comfortably on the c7-square, as it is eyeing the bishop on c4 and it gives us ...Ng4 possibilities. The threat of ...Bxf3 can be surprisingly awkward to deal with. }
14. Nd2
{ With this move, White makes sure that we do not have ...Ng4 and ...Bxf3 ideas. However, it does move the knight to a slightly more passive square. }
