{ As we will often see in this opening, ...h6 will almost always be a good way to meet Bg5. We do not mind the trade on f6, and the inclusion of ...h6 and Bh4 favors us somewhat. We will have an escape square for our king, and we can potentially break the pin with ...g5 as well. }
8. Bh4 d5
