{ This simplifies matters. White sacrifices the bishop to be able to capture the knight on e3 and get rid of the fork that way. }
21... Kxh7 22. Rxe3 Qxg5
{ Black will also develop the light-squared bishop in the foreseeable future and is fine here. The game Li-Xu, Hangzhou 2022 ended in a draw. }
