{ It might seem somewhat odd to play @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp1p1ppp/4pn2/2p5/2PP4/P1P5/4PPPP/R1BQKBNR w KQkq c6 0 6@@EndFEN@@  6.e3  followed by 7.e4, but the point is that since we have played  6...b6  , we now cannot play ...Qa5 as we would against @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp1p1ppp/4pn2/2p5/2PP4/P1P5/4PPPP/R1BQKBNR w KQkq c6 0 6@@EndFEN@@  6.e4  . }
