12... h6 13. Bh4 d5
{ Bolstering the bishop on c4 and taking more control in the center. } 14. e5
g5 15. Bf2 Nd7 16. f4
{ White starts to open up the kingside, but fortunately, we do not have to worry about that. }
16... Qe7
{ We are going to play castle queenside next, where our king will sit quite safely. }
