{ It might seem somewhat counterintuitive to castle kingside, as White is ready to open up the h-file. However, White has no good way to bring more pieces closer to our king, as our e4-pawn restricts their pieces.  Next, we can continue improving our position with ...Nbd7-e5, and ...Bg6 will often be a useful move as well, to make sure the bishop is not hanging. }
