[Result "*"]

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. a3
{ With this move, White stops us from ever going ...Bb4. Next, White wants to play Nc3 and e4, so we will have to take action in the center ourselves. }
3... d5 4. cxd5 exd5 5. Nc3 c6
{ We have a comfortable Carlsbad structure here, as our pieces have easy development. Next on our agenda will be to develop our bishops to f5 and d6, and our knight to d7. }
